statements: SELECT * FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction WHERE energy_produced > 100
SELECT id, production_time FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction WHERE turbine_id = 3 ORDER BY production_time DESC
SELECT AVG(energy_produced) AS avg_energy FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction WHERE production_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT MAX(energy_produced) AS max_energy, turbine_id FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction GROUP BY turbine_id
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction ORDER BY production_time DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT id, energy_produced FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction WHERE energy_produced > 1000
SELECT turbine_id, SUM(energy_produced) AS total_energy_produced FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction GROUP BY turbine_id
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction WHERE turbine_id = 3 ORDER BY production_time
SELECT MAX(energy_produced) AS max_energy_produced, MIN(energy_produced) AS min_energy_produced FROM WindTurbineEnergyProduction
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_data;
SELECT turbine_id, production_rate FROM wind_turbine_data ORDER BY production_rate DESC;
SELECT temperature, production_rate FROM wind_turbine_data WHERE temperature > 50;
SELECT * FROM turbine_location WHERE latitude < 40 AND longitude > -100;
SELECT turbine_id, latitude, longitude FROM turbine_location ORDER BY latitude, longitude DESC;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_data ORDER BY production_rate DESC, temperature ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT wt.turbine_id, COUNT(wt.production_rate) AS production_count, AVG(tl.latitude) AS avg_latitude FROM wind_turbine_data wt INNER JOIN turbine_location tl ON wt.turbine_id = tl.turbine_id GROUP BY wt.turbine_id HAVING production_count > 5;
SELECT tl.latitude, tl.longitude, wt.production_rate FROM turbine_location tl LEFT JOIN wind_turbine_data wt ON tl.turbine_id = wt.turbine_id WHERE tl.latitude >= 40.0 AND wt.production_rate > 100;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_data WHERE temperature < 20 OR production_rate > 500 ORDER BY id ASC;

SELECT SUM(wt.production_rate) AS total_production, AVG(tl.longitude) AS avg_longitude FROM wind_turbine_data wt INNER JOIN turbine_location tl ON wt.turbine_id = tl.turbine_id WHERE tl.longitude < -100 GROUP BY tl.location_id ORDER BY total_production DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT max_power_output, min_power_output FROM wind_turbine_settings WHERE turbine_id = 'ab1234cd-5678-ef90-gh12-ijkl3456mnop'
SELECT * FROM turbine_status WHERE power_output >= 5000.00 ORDER BY wind_speed DESC
SELECT turbine_id, blade_angle FROM turbine_status WHERE status_id IN ('xy7890uv-1234-wx56-yz78-abc9012def34','ef5678uv-9012-gh34-ij56-kl78mn901op')
SELECT * FROM energy_production WHERE date_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-01-02 23:59:59'
SELECT turbine_id, SUM(energy_generated) AS total_energy FROM energy_production GROUP BY turbine_id HAVING total_energy > 10000
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_settings
SELECT turbine_id, rotor_diameter FROM wind_turbine_settings WHERE rotor_diameter > 100
SELECT * FROM turbine_status ORDER BY power_output DESC
SELECT turbine_id, wind_speed, blade_angle FROM turbine_status WHERE wind_speed > 10 AND blade_angle < 45
SELECT * FROM energy_production WHERE date_time >= '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM turbine LIMIT 10;
SELECT location, power_output FROM turbine WHERE status = 'active';
SELECT * FROM energy_production ORDER BY production_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, location FROM power_station WHERE capacity > 1000;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_log WHERE description LIKE '%fault%';
SELECT * FROM turbine WHERE status = 'Active' ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT location, power_output FROM turbine WHERE power_output > 1000 ORDER BY power_output DESC;
SELECT * FROM energy_production WHERE production_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY production_time;
SELECT id, location, capacity FROM power_station WHERE status = 'Operational' ORDER BY capacity ASC;

SELECT turbine.location, energy_production.energy_produced FROM turbine INNER JOIN energy_production ON turbine.id = energy_production.turbine_id WHERE energy_production.energy_produced > 500 ORDER BY energy_production.energy_produced DESC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine ORDER BY production_capacity DESC;
SELECT location, status FROM WindTurbine WHERE status='Active';
SELECT turbine_id, MAX(power_output) AS max_power_output FROM TurbineData GROUP BY turbine_id;
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceLog WHERE maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01' AND maintenance_date <= '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM WeatherData WHERE temperature > 25 AND humidity < 70;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE location = 'New York' ORDER BY production_capacity DESC
SELECT turbine_id, status FROM WindTurbine WHERE production_capacity > 1000 AND status = 'Active'
SELECT MAX(production_capacity) AS max_capacity FROM WindTurbine
SELECT AVG(energy_consumed) AS avg_consumption FROM EnergyConsumption
SELECT w.timestamp, w.temperature, wd.humidity FROM WeatherData w JOIN WeatherData wd ON w.timestamp = wd.timestamp
